name: Shadow portrait
description:
Since the creation of the world, human beings have been afraid of what they do not see, do not understand. 

Here the imagination wants to understand, to find something it knows, so as not to sink into fear and the madness of the unknown. He embodies both the fear and the hope of the human being. He is each of us and no one at the same time.

A great thank you to all for your unwavering support. I hope you will enjoy this work, because I love it.

Roman Guillermo
